{"tid":1649991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我屌哂你班仆街呀","createTime":"2019-10-12T19:22:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T21:06:56.000Z","uid":201148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"285a63041adbb3dae6fe328b9be6c7315f7c236c","tid":1649991,"uid":201148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T19:22:08.000Z","msg":"成個連登都切蛋糕<br />\n聽日開花啦仲講切蛋糕<br />\n切乜撚野咁重要呀<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌哂你地老母</span></span>"},{"pid":"8b20e6041bb4b3a6efeb3d361d266beaa7175417","tid":1649991,"uid":102535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T19:23:27.000Z","msg":"《人手轉載》<br />\n<br />\n希望大家維持嗌五大訴求：<br />\n1.缺一不可本來就有環環相扣既意思，正如林鄭撤回咗條例，都唔會改嗌四大訴求，簡單啲講，呢句野既結果一係5，一係0，冇其他。<br />\n2.解散警隊呢個訴求並唔夠實際同具體，基本上五大訴求達成就已經可以蓋括埋解散警隊既效果，正如一開始第五個訴求係林鄭下台，大家都覺得呢個訴求唔實際，所以改做雙普選，所以，我地係唔需要特登加多一個訴求落去，咁先比到人睇我地一直爭取緊既係具體、可行、實際既訴求。<br />\n解散警隊可以獨立嗌，代表我地對警隊嚴重不滿，但唔好將佢當做第六大訴求。<br />\n3.國際啱啱先開始知到我地爭取緊既係五大訴求而唔係林鄭一句撤回就咁簡單，所以維持五大訴求先比到人一種由始此終都係爭取緊同一樣野既觀感。"},{"pid":"8d514ae53a8c240e8543205b528b4a74fa1c44fc","tid":1649991,"uid":325269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T19:29:24.000Z","msg":"不篤灰 不割蓆唔係口號<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bMrUgfE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbMrUgfE.jpg&h=7e0b4b2a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n8OfK8Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn8OfK8Z.jpg&h=8241555a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4Gc0WfF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4Gc0WfF.png&h=b642bb0b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XmEywO1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXmEywO1.png&h=04d87e0f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PEJvy2m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPEJvy2m.jpg&h=5fa169b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"79edd6ff43663afcffa3fdbefd5444d4075dd5c1","tid":1649991,"uid":248078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T19:35:50.000Z","msg":"推行動po"},{"pid":"c6ba9b0e42e51ec9cc123dc98a4c166b11749f22","tid":1649991,"uid":248078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T19:36:00.000Z","msg":"幫手推"},{"pid":"75a4307ad0c28e0a1bffcba489b1e4327966bdff","tid":1649991,"uid":155784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T21:06:56.000Z","msg":"史記錄，寫上香港最後的民主運動，由一頂綠帽開始，因一個蛋糕結束。<br />\n<br />\n你地唔醜我都醜。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}